The '''Starfly''' was a small, maneuverable single-person [[Starship/Legends|vessel]]. It was equipped with a [[Tractor beam/Legends|tractor beam]] but carried no [[Life support/Legends|life support]] equipment, hence, Starfly [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] were forced to wear self-contained suits while flying the ships. Starflies were piloted by miners in the [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroid]] [[Asteroid field/Legends|belts]] near [[Ithor/Legends|Ithor]].

